The time has come, Commander. You’re about to embark on a new campaign that will require every ounce of your strength, dedication, and bravery. Do your duty in OVERLORD, the latest season of World of Tanks Modern Armor! 

In this D-Day-inspired season, you can earn incredible rewards across 100 stages, including War Chests, Gold, and Premium tanks, while exploring new in-game features with your allies. Join your band of brothers for the D-Day: Sword Beach mode, battle on a revamped map, and explore many new features coming to your console this summer.  

Trust your training and become the hero you’re meant to be in this new season, starting June 3 on PlayStation!

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011452/

Have you ever had the feeling of being trapped in a nightmare with no way of getting out?
Do you want the craziest VR experience on PSVR2?

Take the time for a good horror movie and get ready... For anything!

As a famous adventurer would say, "in survival there are three immutable rules:
Survive, Survive, Survive. And occasionally Run!"

GET OUT! is a demanding game create by very tiny French indie Studio that pays homage to retro horror films.

"Get out!" is an original game derived from the "Very Bad Dreams" Franchise released on PSVR2
Playing a difficult patient locked in a strange mental asylum and experience a day like no other!
Exclusively developed for the PSVR2 with well-worked haptic capabilities (B-Haptics compatible).
Maybe the craziest VR Horror game ever...

#ps5 #psvr2 #psvr2games #getout
